sential ingredient in a snuff used to ease headaches.\r\n\r\nFunctions:\r\nA poultice of Basil leaves can help draw out insect, bee wasp, or snake venom. It can help cure acne, heal abrasions, cuts and gives a persons hair a high shine after it is used as a rinse. Popularly know as basil, Tulsi is an extremely aromatic and stimulating herb. It has many antibacterial, anti-stress, anti-fungal, and antibiotic properties. The aroma of tulsi is conducive to meditation. It is used in many skin treatments, and is particularly helpful in smoothening and softening the skin. Leaves and seeds are used to treat skin problems; roots are used for fever, bee stings, and insect bites. Other uses include treating nausea, motion sickness, gastric and liver disorders, diarrhea, and vomiting. The functions described above are believed to be due to the alkaloids in Basil.\r\nWith abundant vitamins A, D, and B2, as well as the minerals calcium, iron, magnesium and phosphorus, Basil is also used for culinary taste, as well as for medicine.','Basil Extract ','','publish','open','open','','basil-extract-alkaloids-0-20-3hplc','','','2013-09-16 06:26:25','2013-09-16 06:26:25','',0,'http://ansbotanics.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=657',0,'portfolio','',0),(658,2,'2013-08-28 04:53:43','2013-08-28 04:53:43','','Basil Extract Alkaloids','','inherit','open','open','','basil-extract-alkaloids','','','2013-08-28 04:53:43','2013-08-28 04:53:43','',657,'http://ansbotanics.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Basil-Extract-Alkaloids.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(659,2,'2013-08-28 04:54:23','2013-08-28 04:54:23','Product Name: Basil Powder ExtractLatin Name: Ocimum Sanctum\r\nLatin Name: Ocimum Sanctum\r\nChinese Name:Luo Le\r\nSpecification: Alkaloids 0.2%,0.3% HPLC\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\nThis annual herb is from the Lamiaceae family. The name Basil is from the Greek word \"Basileus\" which means \"King\". Basil is also known as St. Joseph wort. As an annual plant with branchy roots, Basil can grow